Enum Language

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Language>
      • com.beaglebuddy.id3.enums.Language
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Language>

    public enum Language
extends java.lang.Enum<Language>
    ISO-639-2 language codes and names. I have found contradictory listings for the ISO 639-2 language codes. For example, the ISO-639-2 language codes listed at this website differs from the previous one.
